def is_bread_on_board(bread:item, board:item):

    symbol is_on_board = on(bread, board)
    return is_on_board

def is_toaster_ready(toaster:item):
    # Ensure the toaster is plugged in and off, ready for use
    symbol is_ready = plugged(toaster) and is_off(toaster)
    return is_ready

behavior slice_bread(bread:item, knife:item, cutting_board:item):
    body:
        achieve on(bread, cutting_board) # Place the bread on the cutting board
        achieve_once inhand(knife) # Hold the knife in hand to slice the bread
        achieve cut(bread) # Slice the bread

behavior toast_bread(sliced_bread:item, toaster:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(sliced_bread, toaster) # Place the sliced bread inside the toaster
        achieve plugged(toaster) # Ensure the toaster is plugged in
        achieve is_on(toaster) # Turn on the toaster
        # Achieve the final goal when the bread is toasted
